name: Dress for Success Vancouver
description: Dress for Success Vancouver is a community empowering women into the workforce by providing them with professional attire, career services, and skills development programs.

name: Vancouver Chinatown Foundation
description: The Vancouver Chinatown Foundation is a registered charity founded in 2011 to honour a culture and community established in Vancouver more than 100 years ago.

name: Greater Vancouver Community Services Society
description: The Greater Vancouver Community Services Society support the independence and well-being of the elderly, people with disabilities, and others who require support to retain or regain health and autonomy.
